    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Music AI Creator</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f8fa;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #24292e;
        }
        p {
            color: #586069;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🎵 Music AI Creator</h1>
    <p>我的第一个 GitHub Pages 站点</p >
    <p>访问地址: <a href=" " target="_blank">https://music-ai-creator.github.io/my-first-project/</a ></p >
</body>
</html>


